---
// アプリ内 AI チャットパネル（F-17、Phase 6）
// パスワード認証 → Anthropic API 経由で候補生成 → GitHub commit で永続化
---

<button type="button" id="chat-toggle" class="chat-toggle" aria-label="AI チャットを開く">
  <span aria-hidden="true">💬</span>
  <span>AI に聞く</span>
</button>

<div id="chat-panel" class="chat-panel" hidden role="dialog" aria-label="AI チャット">
  <header class="chat-header">
    <h2>AI に店舗を聞く</h2>
    <button type="button" id="chat-close" class="chat-close" aria-label="閉じる">×</button>
  </header>

  <div id="chat-auth" class="chat-auth">
    <p>このチャットは閲覧者全員に公開されないため、パスワードでロックされています。</p>
    <input type="password" id="chat-password" placeholder="パスワード" autocomplete="current-password" />
    <button type="button" id="chat-auth-submit">ロック解除</button>
    <p class="chat-auth-error" id="chat-auth-error" hidden></p>
  </div>

  <div id="chat-content" class="chat-content" hidden>
    <div id="chat-messages" class="chat-messages" aria-live="polite"></div>
    <form id="chat-form" class="chat-form">
      <textarea
        id="chat-input"
        placeholder="例: ローマで朝食にいい場所を 3 件教えて"
        rows="2"
        required
      ></textarea>
      <button type="submit" id="chat-send">送信</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
  type Candidate = {
    id?: string;
    name: string;
    city: string;
    area?: string;
    genre: string;
    priceRange?: string;
    lat: number;
    lng: number;
    address?: string;
    visited: boolean;
    url?: string;
    tags?: string[];
    source?: string;
    sourceTrust?: string;
    verdict?: string;
    concerns?: Array<{ type: string; severity: string; note?: string }>;
    highlights?: Array<{ type: string; note?: string }>;
    lastAnalyzed?: string;
  };

  const PASSWORD_KEY = 'italia-gohan-chat-password';

  function getPassword(): string | null {
    return sessionStorage.getItem(PASSWORD_KEY);
  }
  function setPassword(p: string) {
    sessionStorage.setItem(PASSWORD_KEY, p);
  }
  function clearPassword() {
    sessionStorage.removeItem(PASSWORD_KEY);
  }

  function escape(s: string): string {
    return s
      .replace(/&/g, '&amp;')
      .replace(/</g, '&lt;')
      .replace(/>/g, '&gt;')
      .replace(/"/g, '&quot;')
      .replace(/'/g, '&#39;');
  }

  function renderCandidate(c: Candidate, idx: number): string {
    const meta = [c.city, c.area, c.priceRange].filter(Boolean).join(' ・ ');
    const tags = (c.tags ?? []).map((t) => `<span class="chat-tag">${escape(t)}</span>`).join('');
    const verdictBadge = c.verdict
      ? `<span class="chat-verdict chat-verdict-${c.verdict}">${escape(c.verdict)}</span>`
      : '';
    return `
      <div class="chat-candidate" data-idx="${idx}">
        <div class="chat-candidate-head">
          ${verdictBadge}
          <strong>${escape(c.name)}</strong>
        </div>
        <p class="chat-candidate-meta">${escape(meta)} / ${escape(c.genre)}</p>
        ${c.address ? `<p class="chat-candidate-addr">📍 ${escape(c.address)}</p>` : ''}
        ${tags ? `<div class="chat-tags">${tags}</div>` : ''}
        <button type="button" class="chat-add-btn" data-idx="${idx}">＋ リストに追加</button>
      </div>
    `;
  }

  function appendMessage(role: 'user' | 'assistant' | 'system', html: string) {
    const container = document.getElementById('chat-messages');
    if (!container) return;
    const div = document.createElement('div');
    div.className = `chat-msg chat-msg-${role}`;
    div.innerHTML = html;
    container.appendChild(div);
    container.scrollTop = container.scrollHeight;
  }

  let currentCandidates: Candidate[] = [];

  async function send(message: string) {
    const password = getPassword();
    if (!password) return;
    appendMessage('user', escape(message));
    appendMessage('system', '<em>AI 思考中…（Web 検索を含むため 10〜30 秒）</em>');

    try {
      const res = await fetch('/api/chat', {
        method: 'POST',
        headers: { 'content-type': 'application/json', 'x-admin-password': password },
        body: JSON.stringify({ message }),
      });
      // remove loading
      const msgs = document.querySelectorAll('.chat-msg-system');
      const last = msgs[msgs.length - 1];
      if (last) last.remove();

      if (res.status === 401) {
        clearPassword();
        showAuth();
        appendMessage('system', '<em>パスワードが無効です。再入力してください。</em>');
        return;
      }
      const json = await res.json();
      if (!res.ok) {
        appendMessage('system', `<em>エラー: ${escape(json.error ?? 'unknown')}</em>`);
        return;
      }
      const aiMsg = json.message ? `<p>${escape(json.message)}</p>` : '';
      const candidatesHtml = (json.candidates as Candidate[]).map((c, i) => renderCandidate(c, i)).join('');
      const sourcesHtml =
        json.sources && json.sources.length > 0
          ? `<p class="chat-sources">出典: ${(json.sources as string[]).map((s) => `<a href="${escape(s)}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">${escape(new URL(s).hostname)}</a>`).join(', ')}</p>`
          : '';
      currentCandidates = json.candidates ?? [];
      appendMessage('assistant', aiMsg + candidatesHtml + sourcesHtml);
    } catch (e) {
      appendMessage('system', `<em>ネットワークエラー: ${escape(String(e))}</em>`);
    }
  }

  async function saveCandidate(idx: number, btn: HTMLButtonElement) {
    const password = getPassword();
    if (!password) return;
    const c = currentCandidates[idx];
    if (!c) return;
    btn.disabled = true;
    btn.textContent = '送信中…';
    try {
      const res = await fetch('/api/save', {
        method: 'POST',
        headers: { 'content-type': 'application/json', 'x-admin-password': password },
        body: JSON.stringify({ candidate: c }),
      });
      const json = await res.json();
      if (!res.ok) {
        btn.disabled = false;
        btn.textContent = `エラー: ${json.error?.slice(0, 30) ?? 'failed'}`;
        return;
      }
      btn.textContent = `✓ 追加済み (commit ${json.commitSha?.slice(0, 7)})`;
      btn.classList.add('is-saved');
    } catch (e) {
      btn.disabled = false;
      btn.textContent = `ネットワークエラー`;
    }
  }

  function showAuth() {
    document.getElementById('chat-auth')!.hidden = false;
    document.getElementById('chat-content')!.hidden = true;
  }
  function showChat() {
    document.getElementById('chat-auth')!.hidden = true;
    document.getElementById('chat-content')!.hidden = false;
    const input = document.getElementById('chat-input');
    if (input instanceof HTMLTextAreaElement) input.focus();
  }

  function openPanel() {
    document.getElementById('chat-panel')!.hidden = false;
    if (getPassword()) showChat();
    else showAuth();
  }
  function closePanel() {
    document.getElementById('chat-panel')!.hidden = true;
  }

  document.getElementById('chat-toggle')?.addEventListener('click', openPanel);
  document.getElementById('chat-close')?.addEventListener('click', closePanel);

  document.getElementById('chat-auth-submit')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
    const input = document.getElementById('chat-password') as HTMLInputElement;
    const errBox = document.getElementById('chat-auth-error');
    const value = input.value.trim();
    if (!value) return;
    setPassword(value);
    if (errBox) errBox.hidden = true;
    showChat();
  });

  document.getElementById('chat-form')?.addEventListener('submit', (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();
    const input = document.getElementById('chat-input') as HTMLTextAreaElement;
    const msg = input.value.trim();
    if (!msg) return;
    input.value = '';
    send(msg);
  });

  document.getElementById('chat-messages')?.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
    const target = e.target;
    if (!(target instanceof HTMLElement)) return;
    if (target.classList.contains('chat-add-btn')) {
      const idx = Number(target.getAttribute('data-idx'));
      if (Number.isFinite(idx)) saveCandidate(idx, target as HTMLButtonElement);
    }
  });

  document.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {
    if (e.key === 'Escape') {
      const panel = document.getElementById('chat-panel');
      if (panel && !panel.hidden) closePanel();
    }
  });
</script>
